Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,DE : AIKO\NADIEU.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Putain !{\i0}
